<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Thank You Page</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .thank-you-box {
      background-color: #fff;
      color: #000;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 400;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .green-text {
      color: #4EA72E;
    }

    .big-text {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .visit-link {
      color: #4EA72E;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: underline;
      font-size: 20px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .visit-link:hover {
      color: #6a9c45;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="_builder-form">
    <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-lg-12 text-center thank-you-message">
      <div class="thank-you-box">
        <p class="green-text big-text"><strong>Success!</strong></p>
        <p class="green-text big-text"><strong>We have received your registration.</strong></p>

        <p>
          Your application is now pending admin review. We review all submissions to weed out spam and maintain a high-quality experience for members. Most approvals are completed within a few hours.
        </p>

        <p>
          Once approved, you’ll receive an email to set your password and access your account.
        </p>

        <p>
          After you log in, you’ll be able to like, comment, and post, as well as set up your profile.
        </p>

        <p>
          In the meantime, you can freely explore the community and see what members are chatting about!
        </p>

        <p>
          <a href="https://community.republicofgreen.com/" target="_blank" class="visit-link">VISIT COMMUNITY</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
